README : HOW TO DESCLIBE GAMMA INPUT FILE FOR EVENTGENERATOR

In gamma input files, you can define the decay scheme to be simulated.
This file consists of "LEVEL" and "DECAY" defined as follows:

_______________________________________________________________________
LEVEL N P E T

N : ID of level.
P : Populate probability (relative value is OK)
E : Excitation energy of level
T : Halflife of level
_______________________________________________________________________
DECAY I F B

I : ID of initial level
F : ID of final level
B : Branching ratio of ID=I for transition to ID=F
_______________________________________________________________________

